# {{PROJECT_NAME}} Coordination

All active workstreams for {{PROJECT_NAME}}. Each workstream has its
own coordination file with tasks, memos, and change log. Agents are
global — see [AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md) for who's who — and can work
across multiple streams simultaneously.

> **New agent / fresh context?** Read [ONBOARDING.md](ONBOARDING.md) first —
> it walks you through the opening ritual (understand the system,
> find your work via `tayfa-inbox`, read your scratchboard + workstream
> file + linked specs).

